NAME
    Config::SL - Configuration file abstraction for Silver Lining
    applications

ABSTRACT
      use Config::SL;

      $cfg  = Config::SL->new;
      $val  = $cfg->key;
      @vals = $cfg->key;

DESCRIPTION
    This package is responsible for handling Silver Lining configuration
    data. It should make our lives less complex.

    It is an abstraction of Config::ApacheFormat, and looks for the
    configuration file sl.conf in various locations.

